rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A fictional being who appears in comic books.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Character

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book character to a comic book issue where the character has appeared on the cover.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Cover Appearances

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book character to a person who had a role in creating the character. For example, Stan Lee is the creator of Spiderman, the Hulk, and Iron Man.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Creator

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: The issue of the comic book in which the given character first appeared.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: First Appearance of Character

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property relating a comic book character to the fictional universe where most of the adventures of the character occur.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Primary Universe

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book character to series where the character plays a primary role.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Featured Appearances

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book character to comic book stories where the character appears.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Story Appearances

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: People who are responsible for choosing and adding color to the black and white line art in comic books.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Colorist

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book colorist to covers of comic books which he or she colored.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Covers Colored

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book colorist to comic book stories which he or she colored.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Stories Colored

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Stores that specialize in selling comics, graphic novels, and manga.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Books Store

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A relationship type that specifies information about a particular story within an issue of a comic book.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Story Printing

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: The final page number of the story in the issue of the comic book.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: End Page

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the issue of the comic book in which the story appears.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Issue

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: The first page number of the story in the issue of the comic book.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Start Page

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the story that appeared in the comic book issue.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Story

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: People who have a role in creating comic books. For example, Stan Lee is the creator of comic books featuring Spiderman, the Hulk, and Iron Man.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Creator

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a person to the comic book characters created by the person.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Characters Created

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book creator to a series of comic books created by him or her.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Series Created

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: People who have a role in selecting and revising the text and illustrations of comic books.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Editor

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a person to the comic book issues edited by the person.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Issues Edited

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A fictional universe that is the setting of comic book stories.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Fictional Universe

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a fictional universe to the comic book characters who play a major role in the universe.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Universe Characters

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: The publisher that has issues most of the stories set in the given universe. Publishers that have issued only cross-over stories or who have licensed the fictional universe from the primary owner should not be entered as values of this property.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Primary Publisher

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A type containing standard descriptors for the form, style or subject matter of a comic book, e.g. manga, crime comics, etc.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Genre

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a genre to a series of comic books that belong to the genre.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Series

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a genre to comic book stories that belong to the genre.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Stories in the Genre

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A person who uses ink to create refined drawings after a penciller has created the original line drawings in a comic book.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Inker

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a person to the comic book stories inked by the person.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Stories Inked

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a person to the comic book covers inked by the person.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Covers Inked

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A particular number of a comic book.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Issue

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to characters who appear on the cover of the issue.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Characters On Cover

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to a colorist for the issue.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Issue Colorist

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to information about a story that appears in the issue.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Contents

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to its cover price.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Cover Price

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to the date when it was published.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date Of Publication

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to an editor for the issue.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Editor

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to an inker for the issue.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Issue Inker

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to the number corresponding to the issue.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Issue Number

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to a letterer for the issue.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Issue Letterer

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a given comic book issue to the next issue in the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Next issue

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to the comic book series of which the issue is a part.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Issue Series

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to a penciler for the issue.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Issue Penciler

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book issue to its previous issue in the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Previous Issue

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a given comic book issue to the number of copies of the issue printed.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Print Run

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A person who is reponsible for drawing the text in a comic book.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Letterer

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book letterer to a comic book cover that he or she has lettered.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Covers Lettered

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book letterer to a comic book story that he or she has lettered.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Stories Lettered

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A person who creates the original line drawings in a comic book using a pencil. These lines are later refined by the inker and then filled in by the colorist.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Penciler

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book penciler to a comic book story that he or she has penciled.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Books Penciled

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book penciler to a cover of a comic book issue that he or she has penciled.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Covers Penciled

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A company that publishes comic books.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Publisher

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book publisher to a series of comic books that it publishes.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Series Published

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A collection of comic books that are published in a sequence and are intended to form a unit.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Series

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book series to another series that continues the story of the first.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Series Continued by

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates two comic book series when the first continues the story developed in the second.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Continuing Series

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book series to a creator of the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Series Created by

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book series to a character who has a primary role in the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Featured Characters

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book series to the final issue of the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Final Issue

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book series to the first issue of the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: First Issue

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book series to a genre of the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Series Genre

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book series to any issue of the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Series Issue

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book series to the total number of issues published in the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Number Of Issues

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book series to the company that publishes the series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Publisher

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A plot line that appars within a comic book issue. For stories that span multiple issues or even multiple series, see comic_books.story_arc.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Story

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to someone who contributed to the plot but is not the main writer of the story. For the main writer, see comic_books.story.script.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Additional Plotting

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to information about comic book issues where the story appeared.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Story Appearances

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to one of the characters in the story.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Characters

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to one of the colorists for the story.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Colorist

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to the genre of the story.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Genre

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to one of the inkers for the story.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Inker

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to one of the letterers for the story.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Letterer

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to its overall story arc, which is a plot line spanning multiple issues or even series.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Part of Story Arc

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to one of the pencilers for the story.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Penciler

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story to one of the writers of the comic book.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Script

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A story spanning multiple issues or even series of a comic book.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Story Arc

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book story arc to the stories that are part of the arc.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Stories in Story Arc

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity type representing the collection of all comics published primarily on the web. Some webcomics are exclusively on the web, while others are also published in magazines, newspapers, or other mediums.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Webcomic

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: The person who is responsible for the narrative and dialogue of the comic book.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Book Writer

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book writer to comic book stories where he or she has made a secondary contribution.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Additional Plotting Contributions

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that relates a comic book writer to comic book stories where he or she has made a primary contribution.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Comic Books Written
